  <brief_title>Inhaled Furosemide Versus Placebo for Acute Viral Bronchiolitis in Hospitalized Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Inhaled Furosemide Versus Placebo for Acute Viral Bronchiolitis in Hospitalized Infants</official_title>
